Current Draw Estimation:
Calculated the total current draw to ensure the power supply can handle the combined load.
𝐼𝑡𝑜𝑡𝑎𝑙=𝐼𝑠𝑒𝑟𝑣𝑜+𝐼𝑤ℎ𝑒𝑒𝑙+𝐼𝑐𝑎𝑚𝑒𝑟𝑎+𝐼𝑀𝐶𝑈I total=I servo+I wheel +I camera+I MCU
